        "timestamp": "2021-02-17 13:47:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(4 comments)\n\nThis seems to be copied from https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/integration/csit/+/117867 and https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/integration/csit/+/117868, please see my comments on those (looks like a lot of copy-pasted code, have you considered the possibility of refactoring all of these to some common keywords?)\n\nAlso, there's far too much stuff being put under plans directory (they should really never contain anything more that setup.sh, testplan.txt and teardown.sh - everything else should be under scripts, tests or possibly even different repo altogether) but that's a more common problem without clear best practices for things like simulators so maybe we won't solve that one in this commit",
